data.description: Darling home in sought after Rockwood School District. Boasting FOUR bedrooms, NEW kitchen with beautiful white shaker cabinets, subway tile, quartz counters, and stainless appliances that stay with the home. Fresh paint throughout home. New flooring. Newly painted gazebo and shed in fully fenced backyard, complete with patio perfect for outdoor entertaining. Cozy up by the fireplace next to the beautiful bay window. New backdoor. New closet systems in all the closets. This freshly updated home is just ready for you to move in!
